      "message": "Yes, this clip will remove the extended 3*sigma area in skia. Without this clip, the extended 3*sigma area will have the same value as the edge, which makes it looks weird.\n\nIn the case I try to fix in ChromeOS, we should always clip. IIRC, Chrome passes in a src_image already with 3*sigma expanding and intersected with the viewport.",
